{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":9,"arguments_yes_count":0,"arguments_no_count":0,"id":453,"created_at":"2015-10-07T10:55:05+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-07T10:55:05+0200","body":"<p>Dans le cadre de l&#39;apprentissage de la citoyennet&eacute;, l&#39;apprenant doit apprendre &agrave; savoir faire la diff&eacute;rence entre un service loyal et un service qui ne l&#39;est pas.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>Il sera notamment alert&eacute; sur l&#39;exploitation qui peut &ecirc;tre faite &agrave; son insu de ses donn&eacute;es et sur les droits dont il dispose ou non pour g&eacute;rer et prot&eacute;ger ses donn&eacute;es sur ce service.<\/p>","versions_count":0,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":0,"author":{"username":"JEANNAS Jean-Yves","displayName":"JEANNAS Jean-Yves","uniqueId":"jeannasjeanyves","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/429_default_avatar.jpg"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/jeannasjeanyves","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":96,"title":"Section 3","subtitle":"Loyaut\u00e9 des plateformes","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[],"modals":[],"votes":[{"user":{"username":"JEANNAS Jean-Yves","displayName":"JEANNAS Jean-Yves","uniqueId":"jeannasjeanyves","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/429_default_avatar.jpg"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/jeannasjeanyves","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Jeanne Varasco","displayName":"Jeanne Varasco","uniqueId":"jeannevarasco","isAdmin"